oose.thequickapp.UI

Class RectangleView

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.view.View
      • oose.thequickapp.UI.RectangleView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.graphics.drawable.Drawable.Callback, android.view.accessibility.AccessibilityEventSource, android.view.KeyEvent.Callback

    public class RectangleView
extends android.view.View
    This class defines the 4*4 board on the main interface when the phone's screen is on or it boots. The color of grid is cyan, while it turns red when the grid is touched.
    Author:
    zcy1848
